<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Password Reset</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>

    <p>We received a request to reset your password.</p>

    <p><strong>Your reset token:</strong> <code><%= token %></code></p>

    <p>This token is valid until <strong><%= expires %></strong>.</p>

    <p>If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>

    <p>Thanks,<br />Car Rental Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
